{"tid":1416381,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"狗局玩埋今日 坐低諗咗之後嘅方向先 好嗎？","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:55:56.000Z","uid":29994,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba7c39981731e3d3c1b1fd4078bf7c27ef90d51","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"認真 現階段我唔認為有好大意義<br />\n你話<span style=\"font-size: small;\">捉狗</span> 入<span style=\"font-size: small;\">去劫槍</span> <br />\n呢啲有意義過喺出面打飛機<br />\n裝備打完<br />\n兵器練完 （<span style=\"color: red;\">火魔法</span>，<span style=\"color: teal;\">冷兵器</span>）<br />\n啲氣出咁啲之後<br />\n<br />\n係時候對準返目標<br />\n冷靜落嚟 諗下之後點玩<br />\n<br />\n呢個政府唔會坐以待弊<br />\n無時無刻都諗緊點搞掂我哋 搞死呢場運動<br />\n<br />\n係時候要諗下點樣令前線有系統啲 協調啲 點升級<br />\n諗下和理非嘅定位<br />\n諗下更多不合作運動<br />\n諗下點先可以做啲嘢令林鄭條仆街知我哋係至死方休<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"0535bb3c0f994dc10c6883ec95a780498771b5ce","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"415a009972d6a19841eda3295f7b34857a3735fe","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac88b253dd6ebae8c7924efaacaec2029862b0af","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cfd99f41dbf27afa50269dda98ae14fe54cca1cb","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"babd6a2d007ecc15da32f8a39d9994498b591830","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9264cf118e10532e45adce1991dab455dba1c1d5","tid":1416381,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f6df4ca092afdcf829cdd5da44e2003